room_title: Escape room "The Sanitorium" by Southernmost Escape in Key West
room_address: 2782 N Roosevelt Blvd. Key West, FL 33040
room_description: The Sanitorium is an abandoned early 1900’s hospital that once housed people dying of tuberculosis and is assumed to be haunted. It is well known that there have been recent disappearances of tourists who were last seen near the Sanitorium, now you have found yourself inside, with the door mysteriously locked behind you. You have 60 minutes to escape before you’re never seen again…
